WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
How would you prove you are a male, if everyone insists on treating you like a female.


00:00:05.250 --> 00:00:07.290
What has this got to do with Jesus?


00:00:07.290 --> 00:00:08.810
Here is some perspective.


00:00:08.810 --> 00:00:12.890
You move to a strange town, where everyone is assigned a gender.


00:00:12.890 --> 00:00:16.080
You know you are a man, but they assign you female.


00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:20.080
Rather than argue, you choose to live the life of a male.


00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:22.480
You marry a woman and impregnate her.


00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:24.990
You then win a gold medal in male wrestling.


00:00:24.990 --> 00:00:31.700
This so angered the same authorities who assigned you the female gender, that they accuse you of living as man.


00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:34.570
Is there a better way to prove that you are a man?


00:00:34.570 --> 00:00:37.210
Now what has this got to do with Jesus, you say?


00:00:37.210 --> 00:00:47.210
Well for that you have to watch the full video on Live Above 3D.


